\id 2TI - Mpoto Bible Version
\h 2 Timoseo
\toc1 Balua ja kabele jaka Paulo kwaka Timoseo
\toc2 2 Timoseo
\toc3 2 Timo
\mt2 Balua ja kabheli jaka Paulo kwa
\mt1 Timoseo
\imt1 Ulongulelo
\ip Chitabu cha kabheli chaka Timoseo nde baluwa ja kabheli yeilembakiki na Mtumi Paulo kujenda kwaka mbolwa waki Timoseo. Baluwa ja kabheli jaka Timoseo jakalembakiki pambipi na ujomukelu wa matamu ghaka Paulo. Mu chikahi chenihechi, Paulo akabhi muchifungo ku muchi wa ku Loma (Sula 1:16). Paulo akabhi na ujonganu wa pambipi nakanopi na Timoseo, na mala pamaheli akundohiki mwana waki (Filimoni 2:22, 1 Timoseo 1:2, 18).
\ip Jenjenu nde jimu ja baluwa nchechi kuhuma kwaka Paulo ambayu ikalembakiki kwa bhandu bheni, wala nga kwa likanisa. Baluwa yengi hitatu nde 1 Timoseo, na Tito na Filimoni. Chikahi baluwa ja kabheli jaka Timoseo pajalembakiki, Bhakristo mu inchi ja Kiloma bhakabhi bhang'ahakika. Iwezikana nde kwa ndandi jeniheji Paulo akabhi muchifungo, na kunjomalake Timoseo ahinakyaje paapetela mambu ghaghanonwipe. Ngati mokubhi mu 1 Timoseo, Paulo ampekeha Timoseo malakalilu ghamaheli kubhokana na bhabhola bha upuhe (1 Timoseo 1:16-18). Ampwaghila kabheti Timoseo kubha palongi ja mwanja unakubya na chikahi cha kunonopa na cha mang'ahiku (Sula 3:1).
\iot Ghaghabhihomu
\io1 Paulo atumbula kwa kundamukila Timoseo (Sula 1:1-2) na kabheti anjeghela mtima (Sula 1:3-18).
\io1 Kabheti Paulo anjomalakela Timoseo kubha wa kuhinakila na wa ukangamalu (Sula 2:1-13).
\io1 Baada ja panihapa ampekeha malaghalakilu gha papamu (Sula 2:14-26).
\io1 Kabheti andakalila panani ja mapitalilu gha mambu ghaghahika, na kundangiha indela jamboni ja kujepana naghu (Sula 3:1-4:8).
\io1 Paulo ajomulela kwa kumpekeha Timoseo malaghalakilu kwaka Timoseo mweni (Sula 4:9-24).
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nepani Paulo, mtumi waka Kristo Yesu kwa mapalu ghaka Chapanga nahuli ndangaza chilanga chela cha womi chechibhi kwa kulombana na Kristo Yesu.
\p 
\v 2 Nukulembe wehapa wa Timoseo wa mwanangu mpalu:
\p Nukulobhela chihomu, na chiha na lukwali, yeihuma kwaka Chapanga Atati na kwaka Kristo Yesu Bambo witu.
\s1 Uchengulu na kujeghaleka mtima
\p 
\v 3 Nunchengu Chapanga, jonunjojabhela kwa zamili jinyahi ngati mobhakatendili bhazee bhangu. Nunchengu Chapanga panunkomboka ikilu na muhi mu malobhu ghangu.
\v 4 Naghakomboka maholi ghako, na ndokulela namaa kukubhona nahuli mbata kutwelakewa chiheku.
\v 5 Ngomboka uhobhalelu waku wa chakaka, uhobhalelu ghoakabhi nau ambuja waku Loisi na mabhu waku Eunike. Nanatu bhelabhela nhobhalela sajenu wehapa ubhi nau uhobhalelu hoghu.
\v 6 Kwa ndandi jenu nukukombukela ukokakyaje nhupu yela yaka Chapanga, yeibhekakiki mkati jaku panakakubhekili mabhoku ghangu na kukulobhela.
\v 7 Maghambu Chapanga ngacheakatupekihi Roho wa choghohi, nambu Roho wa makili, wa upalu na wa mtima wa kulijemalela.
\p 
\v 8 Henu ngawibhona ihoni kundandila Bambo witu, wala ngawibhona ihoni kwa ndandi jangu nepani nengongakiki kwa ndandi jaki, nambu uhinakalyaje mang'ahiku papamu na nepani kwa ndandi ja Malobhi Manyahi, kwa makili ghaupekewa na Chapanga.
\v 9 Jombi akatukengalili na akatulohiki tutamaje matamu mahuhu, nga kwa kulengana na matendu ghitu ghamboni nambu ngati bhela moakapali mweni na chihomu chaki. Chihomu hechi tupekiwi muka Kristo Yesu mangani ja kutumbula kwa chikahi,
\v 10 nambu sajenu chiyekuliwi kwitu kwa kuhika kwaki Mkengalela witu, Kristo Yesu. Jombi ayoningi makili gha nyiwa, na kwa indela ja Malobhi Manyahi auyekwi womi wanga na nyiwa.
\p 
\v 11 Chapanga anhawi mya mtumi na mbola kwa ndandi ja kutangaza Malobhi Manyahi.
\v 12 Kwa ndandi jeniheji nde ng'ahika ntundu ghoni. Nambu ngachemona ihoni kwa ndandi nummanyi jombi jonunhobhalela, bhela nhobhale nakanopi kubha aweza kuchilenda wichu chela cheambekihe mbaka Lichobha lela.
\v 13 Kamulakya wichu malobhi ghala ghaghabhi na womi ghanukubholiki, na uhighalya mu uhobhalelu na upalu ghoubhi mu kulombana na Kristo Yesu.
\v 14 Ulilendaje lijambu lela lamboni leupekiwi kwa makili ghaka Roho Mhuhu joatama mkati jitu.
\p 
\v 15 Wehapa umanyi kubha bhandu bhokapi mu Asia bhanekike, hata Figelo na Helimogene bhanekike.
\v 16 Bambo abhabhonila chiha bhandu bha munyumba jaka Onesifolo, kwa ndandi akanihekihi mala pamaheli, na ngacheaweni ihoni chikahi panakabhi muchifungu,
\v 17 nambu paakahikiki pani pa Loma, akanondiki namaa mbaka akambatike.
\v 18 Bambo na ampekyaje kupata chiha chaki Lichobha lela! Na wehapa umanyi wichu ntundu moakanyangatili ku Efeso hoku.
\c 2
\s1 Linjolinjoli ndongwana waka Yesu Kristo
\p 
\v 1 Henu, wehapa wa mwanangu, Chapanga akupekya ukangamalu mu chihomu chetupata mu kulombana na Kristo Yesu.
\v 2 Na mabholu ghala ghawajowini nakatangazaje palongi ja bhalandila bhamaheli, uwapekya bhandu bhalongwana bhabhiweza kubhabhola bhandu bhangi bhelabhela.
\p 
\v 3 Hinakyaje mang'ahiku papamu na nepani ngati linjolinjoli ndongwana waka Kristo Yesu.
\v 4 Linjolinjoli kungondu alijepa na lihengu la matamu gha kawaida, nahuli aweza kunyambiha jola joambekiki kubha linjolinjoli.
\v 5 Bhelabhela mundu joakembela na bhajaki mu imbelu, ngacheaweza kujopale nhupu ja ushindi ngati ngacheakajengali shelia ja imbelu.
\v 6 Ndemi joahenga lihengu nakanopi nde joapalika kubha wa kutumbula kupata mahunu.
\v 7 Holalyaje namaa ghangani ghanukupwaghila kwa ndandi Bambo anaakupekya umanyi mu mambu ghanihagha ghokapi.
\p 
\v 8 Unkombukaje Yesu Kristo, joakahyokiki kuhuma kwa bhakuwa, joakabhi wa lubheleku lwaka Daude, ngati moghapwaghi Malobhi Manyahi ghandangaza.
\v 9 Na kwa ndandi ndangaza Malobhi Manyahi, nepani ng'ahika na kukongakeka muchifungo ngati muhakau. Nambu Lilobhi laka Chapanga ngacheliweza kukongakeka muchifungo.
\v 10 Kwa bhela nhinakila mambu ghokapi kwa ndandi ja bhahaghulika bhaka Chapanga, nahuli na bhombi bhapata ukengaleku ghoubhi muka Kristo Yesu, papamu na ulumbalilu wa mileli.
\v 11 Lendenu nde lilobhi la chakaka:
\q1 “Ngati anatupotili papamu naku,
\q1 anatutamaje kabhete papamu naku.
\q1 
\v 12 Ngati anatuhinakili,
\q1 bhelabhela anatutawalaje papamu naku.
\q1 Na ngati anatunkaniki jombi,
\q1 najombi bhelabhela anaatukana tepani.
\q1 
\v 13 Ngati tepani anatubhi ngatwalongwana,
\q1 jombi atamakila kubha ndongwana,
\q1 kwa ndandi ngacheaweza kung'anambuka kwa ghala ghaakapwaghike.”
\s1 Mhenga lihengu joajetakaliwi na Chapanga
\p 
\v 14 Ubhakombukya bhandu mambu ghanihagha na kubhalakalila palongi jaka Chapanga, bhakotuka kulochana panani ja malobhi ghani. Kulochana hoku ngachekupalika, nambu kuleta pena uyonangeku ukolongwa kwa bhala bhabhajowana.
\v 15 Ukangamalaje kulilangi kubha ujetakaliwi na Chapanga, ngati muhenga lihengu joahenga lihengu laki koni ngachealibhone ihoni lihengu laki na ambaju abhola wichu ubholu wa chakaka waka Chapanga.
\v 16 Ulijepaje na malobhi mahakau, na gha king'ang'a, maghambu kwa ghanihagha ghajonjuke kubhabheka bhandu kutali na Chapanga.
\v 17 Mabholu gha ntundu ghonihoghu ghajaghanila ngati chilonda changakulama na chechikula hyegha. Pachilanda ja bhandu bhabhabholiki ghanihagha abhi Himenayo na Fileto.
\v 18 Bhanihabha bhajilekiki indela ja chakaka, na kuyonanga uhobhalelu wa bhandu bhangi kwa kupwagha eti uhyoheku witu ujomwili kutendakeka.
\v 19 Nambu luhuli lwaka Chapanga lujemiki kwa ukangamalu, na panani jaki palembakiki ana: “Bambo abhamanyi bhabhabhi bhaki,” na “Kila joapwagha kubha nepani nde waka Bambo na aulekaje uhakau.”
\p 
\v 20 Mu nyumba ngolongwa kubhi na mbale na yombu ya kila ntundu: Yengi ilenganakiki kwa madini gha feza na zahabu, yengi ya mikongu na lutopi, yengi ya kutumika kwa utopelu na yengi kutumika panga utopelu.
\v 21 Bhela anakubhi mundu aligholwili kwa kulibheka kutali kuhuma mu hyombu yela yanga utopelu, anakubha chombu cha kupata utopelu, ahaghuliwi na kunyambiha Bambo waki, na alenganakiki kwa kila lihengu lelibhi lambone.
\v 22 Utilaje utokulelu uhakau wa ukombu, ukangamala kujengalela kutama ngati moapali Chapanga, uhobhalelu, upalu na lukwali papamu na bhala bhabhundoha Bambo kwa mtima wamboni.
\v 23 Ulijepaje na malalukilu gha ching'ang'a na ghangakubha na ndandi, maghambu umanyi kubha ghanihagha ghaleta kulochana.
\v 24 Kabheti ngacheipalika mtumika waka Bambo kubha na milomu, nambu impalika akubha mpole kwa bhandu bhokapi, joaweza kubhola na joahinakila,
\v 25 abhalakalya kwa upole bhandu bhala bhabhapengana naku, nahuli ngati anaiwezakini, Chapanga abhapekya mbekenyu ja kung'anambuka na kughaleka mahoku na kuumanya uchakaka.
\v 26 Panihapa maholalelu ghabhu anaghalamuka kabhete, na bhombi anabhalemikaje mu chimbenda chaka Muhakau, ambachu bhanihabha bhakapendakaliwi naku, na kubhatenda bhapata kutenda mapalu ghaki.
\c 3
\s1 Machobha gha ujomukelu
\p 
\v 1 Ukombuka kubha, mu machobha gha ujomukelu anakubya na chikahi cha mang'ahiku makolongwa.
\v 2 Maghambu bhandu anabhakubha bha kulipala bheni, bhabhapala mbija, bhabhapala kulilumbalila, bhabhabhi na ing'omu, bhabhuntondola Chapanga, bhangakubhatii bhabheleka bhabhu, bhangakubha na uchengulu, bhangakubha bhahuhu,
\v 3 bhangakubha na upalu, bhangakupala kujongana, bhabhakopunganela, bhangakulihibhalakila matokuelu ghabhu na bhakale, bhangakupala ghambone,
\v 4 bhabhang'anambuka bhajabhu, bhabhabhi na ing'omu, bhabhatweli kulibhona, bhabhapala kutama matamu mahakau kuliku kumpala Chapanga.
\v 5 Kwa kunja bhabhonikana ngati bhandu bhabhunjojabhe Chapanga, nambu bhaghakana makili ghaki. Ulijepaje na bhandu bha ntundu ghonihoghu.
\v 6 Bhakumu bhabhu bhajenda mu nyumba ya bhandu na kubhakolowa akambomba bhang'ang'a nahuli bhabhajowanya bhombe, akambomba bhabhabhi na hibwahila ya mahoku na kulonguheka na ntundu wokapi wa utokulelu uhakau.
\v 7 Akambomba bhanihabha bhalibhola machobha ghokapi, nambu ngachebhaweza kuuhikila umanyi wa chakaka ng'o.
\v 8 Bhandu bhanihabha bhaukaniki uchakaka ngati Yane na Yamble mobhakumpengi Musa, bhelabhela bhandu bhanihabha bhapengana na chakaka jela. Bhanihabha nde bhandu bhabhabhi na malangu ghaghayonangiki, na bhakanakiki kwa mambu gha uhobhalelu.
\v 9 Nambu ngabhawezi kujendalela nakanopi maghambu ung'ang'a wabhu anaubhonikana palanga ja bhandu bhokapi. Nde mokukabheli kwaka Yane na Yamble.
\s1 Malaghalakilu gha kujomulela
\p 
\v 10 Nambu wehapa wa Timoseo, ughajengalyaje mabholu ghangu, na ntundu mondamila, na chembalikaje mu matamu ghangu, uhobhalelu wangu, uhinakalilu wangu, upalu wangu, na kulendalela kwangu,
\v 11 mang'ahiku na kulagha. Ughamanyi mambu ghaghambatiki ku muchi wa ku Antiokia, ku Ikonio na ku Listila hoku. Nakahinaki mang'ahiku ghokapi nambu Bambo akangengalili mu ghanihagha ghokapi.
\v 12 Kila mundu joapala kutama matamu gha uhuhu mu kulombana na Kristo Yesu anang'ahikaje,
\v 13 nambu bhandu bhahakau na bhabhakolowa anabhapetalyaje kubha bhahakau, bhakakoluwaji na koni bheni bhakoluweka.
\v 14 Nambu wehapa utamaje mu uchakaka ghola ghoukalibholiki na kuhobhalela nakanope. Kwa ndandi ubhamanyi bhala bhabhukubholike,
\v 15 nanau ukombukaje kutumbu umwana waku ughamanyi Malembu Mahuhu ambaghu ghaweza kukupekeha mbulau nahuli ukengaliwaje kwa indela ja uhobhalelu kwaka Kristo Yesu.
\v 16 Kila lilembu lelibhi na mbomu jaka Chapanga lilenganela mu kubholela uchakaka, kulakalila na kubhalangiha bhandu mahakau ghabhu, na kubhalongoha bhatamaje mu matamu ghamboni,
\v 17 nahuli mundu waka Chapanga abya na kila chindu chechipalika kwa kuntumaki jombi, nahuli apata kutenda kila lihengu lamboni.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Nukulaghalaki palongi jaka Chapanga, na palongi jaka Kristo Yesu, joanatemulaje bhandu bhabhabhi bhomi na bhabhapotile, na kwa ndandi ahika kutawala akabya Nkolongwa:
\v 2 Ubhatangazya bhandu ubholu hoghu, ubya wichu kwa chikahi cha kupalika au chikahi changakupalika, kanakyaje, kenjukyaje na ubhajeghala mtima kwa uhinakilu na kubhabhola kwa uhinakalilu wokapi.
\v 3 Maghambu chikahi anachihikaje bhandu anabhakanaje kughajowanela mabholu gha chakaka gha womi, nambu anabhajengalyaje utokulelu wabhu bhene na kuwongana bhabhola bhamaheli bhapata kubhapwaghila mambu ghala pena ambaghu makutu ghabhu ghapala kughajowana.
\v 4 Anabhakanaje kuujowana uchakaka, anabhang'anambukyaje hadisi ya upuhe.
\v 5 Nambu wehapa ukubha mihu chikahi chokapi, hinakalyaje mang'ahiku, tenda lihengu la kutangaza Malobhi Manyahi, jomulakyaje ghaghapalika mu lihengu lako.
\p 
\v 6 Kwa upambala wangu nepani mi pambipi namaa kubhohakeka ngati nyambiku ja kupongola, na chikahi cha kupotela kwangu chiheghalile.
\v 7 Ngomini ngondu wichu, mwanja nyomwile, na uhobhalelu nuulendike.
\v 8 Sajenu nendale kupekewa litaji la kutama matamu gha kujetakalewa palongi jaka Chapanga. Bambo mtemula wambone, anaambekya nhupu heji Lichobha lela, wala nga nepani pena, nambu na bhandu bhokapi kabhete ambabhu bhalendalili kwa chilolu kubhonikana kwaki.
\s1 Paulo andaghalaki Timoseo
\p 
\v 9 Kangamalaje uhika kwangu manyata.
\v 10 Kwa ndandi Dema, kwa kuupala ndema, anekiki na kujenda ku Sesalonike. Kleske apiti ku Galatia na Tito apiti ku Dalimatia.
\v 11 Luka kanjika jaki nde joabhi pambane papamu na nepane. Untola Mako uhika naku kwa ndandi aweza kunyangatila mu lihengu langu.
\v 12 Nuntumiki Tikiko ku Efeso hoku.
\v 13 Pawihikaje unetilaje likoti langu lenililekiki kwaka Kuplo kola ku Tiloa, na bhelabhela unetila hitabu, nakanopi hitabu yela yeilenganakiki kwa chingokolu.
\p 
\v 14 Alekizanda, mponda choma jola akandendili uhakau ukolongwa. Bambo anaandepaje kwa ndandi ja ghala ghaatendike.
\v 15 Ulilingalya naku kwa ndandi akaupengiki nakanopi ubholu witu.
\p 
\v 16 Panakabhi nilikengalela kwa mala ja kutumbula njeta mundu joakajemiki upambala wangu, nambu bhokapi bhakanekiki, nundobha Chapanga ngaabhalangila lihoku kwa lijambu leniheli.
\v 17 Nambu Bambo akajemiki upambala wangu akanyeghili makili, nahuli nabhatangazya bhandu ubholu waki kwa ukangamalu, nahuli bhandu bha mataifa ghokapi bhapata kuujowana. Nepani ngengaliwi kuhuma mu nyiwa ngati kukengalewa kuhuma mu ndomu wa lihimba.
\v 18 Bambo anangengalyaje na mambu ghokapi mahakau, na kumbeleka lukwali mbaka mu Ukolongwa waki wa kunani kumahunde. Alumbalika jombi mileli na mileli! Amina.
\s1 Ulamukilu wa kujomulela
\p 
\v 19 Mubhalamukyaje Pulisila na Akila na bhokapi bha munyumba jaka Onesifolo.
\v 20 Elasto akahighalili ku Kolinso, na Tilofimo nundekiki ku Mileto kwa ndandi akabhi mtamwa.
\v 21 Kangamalaje uhika mangani ja chikahi cha imbepu.
\p Eubulo, na Pude na Lino na Klaudia bhukulamukila papamu na bhalongu bhokapi bhabhunhobhalela Kristo.
\p 
\v 22 Bambo akubha papamu na roho jako.
\p Chihomu chaka Chapanga chikubha papamu na mwehapa mabhokapi. Amina.
